{"tid":381334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黐陳嘉儀跳辣身舞！傷殘鄧兆尊頂得住","createTime":"2017-08-30T23:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T01:59:38.000Z","uid":81228,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c875b451cf82b64d6f58fb625237e14690c5e1b","tid":381334,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T23:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170831060109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170831060109&h=c5a51589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撞傷嘴唇的鄧兆尊自稱是傷殘人士，面對陳嘉儀的辣身舞，強調頂得住！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170831060109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170831060109&h=9dbbbca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧兆尊因拍節目撞傷嘴唇。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170831060109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170831060109&h=1c9ed986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為支持陳嘉儀，鄧兆尊挺身而出！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_04b.jpg?20170831060109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20170831060109&h=2d86eef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧兆尊話咁樣都頂得住。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_05b.jpg?20170831060109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20170831060109&h=aca38bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳嘉儀全力出擊！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_06b.jpg?20170831060109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20170831060109&h=f4bd22fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳嘉儀的辣身舞！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_07b.jpg?20170831060109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20170831060109&h=759847d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳嘉儀<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_08b.jpg?20170831060109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20170831060109&h=968d4c10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳嘉儀、鄧兆尊<br />\n<br />\n藝人鄧兆尊在荔枝角為𡃁模陳嘉儀寫真記者會撐場。擁有34D上圍的陳嘉儀以性感打扮拋胸示人，二人大跳辣身舞，鄧兆尊定力十足，頂得住。<br />\n<br />\n被問跳辣身舞時可會被對方火辣身材吸引？鄧兆尊笑說：「唔係好辣身啫，我平時接觸都係咁上下，冇乜特別，如果早十年就好難講喇。（依傢定力夠？）又唔係，不嬲都冇。（女朋友們會呷醋？）所以咪唔嚟囉，相形見絀。（佢哋好忙呀？）唔係，我好忙，最近拍節目又撞埋牆整親個嘴，已經好番啲。（咪唔可以錫錫囉？）最好啦，我依家傷殘，唔好搞我啦！（女朋友們輪住照顧你？）咪逼我搽嘢囉。」<br />\n<br />\n鄧兆尊又透露明天要為節目拍攝跳傘：「我都有問唔跳得唔得，唔係我唔想跳，係我屋企人話唔好。（近排屋企係咪賣出物業？）冇，我銀行戶口都冇進賬，唔理喇，帶唔走嘅嘢使乜咁緊張。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fbkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001.html&d=IUd5jLMePWSn6jkrzwc9WNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a032be1f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4c1d21fc8611faa16fe3555c376aeea74722e487","tid":381334,"uid":20524,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:00:32.000Z","msg":"陳嘉儀係邊位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"309cea456d42c2a986b58443995040d9f3e01da7","tid":381334,"uid":125665,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳嘉儀係邊位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪陳嘉儀囉"},{"pid":"dbc6120e4de47bd61b3d0b9fecb0754e4eadb9a3","tid":381334,"uid":13169,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:06:27.000Z","msg":"踢甲組？"},{"pid":"53e6193d13147d496b98a0198e74e206e09fe617","tid":381334,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:08:44.000Z","msg":"點解我生得咁靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6977e8021d7809c3b52d24f157ea451157b5205","tid":381334,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:10:38.000Z","msg":"呢個做左人呀媽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a576e4c75dbf1d4c364607b574e6a0352ec3a5","tid":381334,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_08b.jpg?20170831060109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830181354844-0830_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20170831060109&h=968d4c10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebbb2e454767af0f15cb30dffb17a3fbd9427699","tid":381334,"uid":3180,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:16:21.000Z","msg":"（女朋友們會呷醋？）所以咪唔嚟囉，相形見絀。