/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830190335635-0830_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170830210629\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830190335635-0830_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170830210629&h=22c73723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己都唔好意思睇番，究竟有幾咁性感？<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830190335635-0830_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170830210629\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830190335635-0830_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170830210629&h=a3e25204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳嘉儀<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830190335635-0830_00862_001_04b.jpg?20170830210629\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830190335635-0830_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20170830210629&h=92fa6573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳嘉儀<br />\n<br />\n擁有34D上圍的𡃁模陳嘉儀以性感低胸裙拋胸在荔枝角為寫真舉行記招，她請來鄧兆尊與她大跳辣身舞。<br />\n<br />\n陳嘉儀的寫真有不少大膽性感晒股、祼露相片，她說：「有大細書兩本，比普通寫真超級性感，有啲踩界，真空、透視、全祼都有，送嗰本細書仲激，自己都唔好意思睇。」講到與鄧兆尊跳辣身舞，她表示初時也感尷尬，但他很有風度表示會遷就我去跳舞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/bkn-20170830190335635-0830_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fbkn-20170830190335635-0830_00862_001.html&d=IUd5jLMePWSn6jkrzwc9WNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=7725ae55\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/bkn-20170830190335635-0830_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f49040fab42c8a746a62c9190ef4f00815f220d9","tid":381334,"uid":69261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/90qiwlzm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F90qiwlzm&h=cb996f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />